data.rationale:
This module parse a string (or a list), extract each element and
    process theses elements through a RPN (Reverse Polish Notation)
    processor. This processor offer operators in these range:
    ARITHMETIC, RATIONAL, LOGICAL, STRING, STACK, OTHER, REGEX At this
    time, 67 operators are implemented. It is more than a Math module
    (REGEX, TEST, IF...), it is a relatively complete parser.
